  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable
    public class Robot
extends edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.TimedRobot
    The main class representing the Robot Has no function code, but as an exception stores single instances of major mechanisms/subsystems and control systems as instance variables, accessible statically though the runningRobot Robot object

      • robotInit

        public void robotInit()
        Runs once every time the robot initializes. It's a good idea to put button initialization calls here or other things that need subsystems but should be initialized before the robot starts.
